//*==================================================================*          
//* STEP0010 : UTILDB2_UNLDIAUL                                                 
//*==================================================================*          
//STEP0010 EXEC PGM=IKJEFT1B,DYNAMNBR=20,                                       
//         COND=(0,NE)                                                          
//AJOUDB2  INCLUDE MEMBER=DB2LIB                                                
//SYSPUNCH DD  SYSOUT=*                                                         
//SYSTSPRT DD  SYSOUT=*                                                         
//SYSPRINT DD  SYSOUT=*                                                         
//SYSUDUMP DD  SYSOUT=*                                                         
//SYSTSIN  DD  DATA,DLM=#$                                                      
 DSN SYSTEM(DBP8)                                                               
 RUN  PROGRAM(DSNTIAUL) PLAN(DSNTIAUL) PARMS('SQL') -                           
      LIB('CDS9.DB2.DBP8.RUNLIB.LOAD')                                          
#$                                                                              
//SYSIN    DD  DATA,DLM=#$                                                      
    SELECT TDPRNFOY                                                             
    , TDPRNCONT                                                                 
    , TDPRNCARTE                                                                
    , TDPRNDT                                                                   
    , TDPRNSOC                                                                  
    , TDPRCPOSA                                                                 
    , TDPRCPRODCOM                                                              
    , CASE                                                                      
         WHEN TDCHMCHG IS NOT NULL                                              
              THEN TDPRMCRD + TDCHMCHG                                          
              ELSE TDPRMCRD                                                     
      END                                                                       
    , TDPRMSREC                                                                 
    , CASE                                                                      
         WHEN TDCHMCHG IS NOT NULL                                              
              THEN TDPRMCRD + TDCHMCHG - TDPRMSREC                              
              ELSE TDPRMCRD - TDPRMSREC                                         
      END                                                                       
    , TDPRNCC                                                                   
    , TDPRCTYPEPROD                                                             
    , INT(CASE                                                                  
             WHEN TDPRBMENS > 0 THEN TDPRBMENS - TDPRBRGEAT                     
             WHEN TDPRBMENS =0  THEN  -8                                        
          END                                                                   
          )                                                                     
    ,SUBSTR(DIGITS(TDPRNCC),7,3)                                                
    , TDPRNQUANT                                                                
    , CASE                                                                      
         WHEN TDCHMCHG IS NOT NULL                                              
              THEN TDPRMMENS + TDCHMCHG                                         
              ELSE TDPRMMENS                                                    
      END                                                                       
    , TDPRCPAIEMENT                                                             
    FROM PDEU.TBDOPRN                                                           
    LEFT JOIN PDEU.TBDOCHG                                                      
      ON   TDCHNFOY    = TDPRNFOY                                               
      AND  TDCHNCONT   = TDPRNCONT                                              
      AND  TDCHNCARTE  = TDPRNCARTE                                             
      AND  TDCHNDT     = TDPRNDT                                                
    WHERE  TDPRNSOC  NOT IN  (250, 260);                                        
#$

//LISTDAT  DD  SYSOUT=*

//SYSIN    DD  DATA,DLM=#$                                                      
 SELECT CHAR(' TBDOPRN '                                                        
    !!SUM(CASE COLTYPE                                                          
    WHEN 'DECIMAL'     THEN (LENGTH / 2) + 1                                    
    WHEN 'DATE'        THEN 10                                                  
    WHEN 'TIMESTMP'    THEN 26                                                  
    WHEN 'TIME'        THEN 8                                                   
    WHEN 'VARCHAR'     THEN LENGTH + 2                                          
    ELSE LENGTH END ))                                                          
  FROM SYSIBM.SYSCOLUMNS                                                        
 WHERE TBCREATOR = 'PDEU'                                                       
   AND TBNAME = 'TBDOPRN'                                                       
   AND NAME NOT LIKE '%ROWCHANGE'                                               
 WITH UR;                                                                       
#$
